    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_5798-5837",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5798-5837",
      "markText": "但，对我而言，妻子与爱人完全是两码事。即使我已有妻子，也未曾忘却对爱人的怨恨。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5798&rangeEnd=5837",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5798&rangeEnd=5837"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_1980-2055",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1980-2055",
      "markText": "她的犬齿又白又大，笑的时候，唇缘碰在那对犬齿上，形成一道谜样的曲线。她的右颊上点缀着一颗大黑痣，两相呼应，绽放出一种无以名状、既温柔又惹人怜爱的表情。",
      "totalCount": 364,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_12869-12913",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "12869-12913",
      "markText": "即使是现在，你正在阅读这封信的当下，作为你影子的我，依旧躲在某个角落眯起眼睛凝望着你呢！",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12869&rangeEnd=12913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12869&rangeEnd=12913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_19760-19817",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "19760-19817",
      "markText": "静子似乎也在等待这个时机，她向座上宾客颔首示意后，迅速跟在我身后，等到四下无人，轻唤我一声“老师”，随即紧抱着我。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=19760&rangeEnd=19817",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=19760&rangeEnd=19817"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_8216-8279",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8216-8279",
      "markText": "他的推理小说篇篇内容血腥、阴险邪恶，既可怕又令人厌恶，让人一读即寒毛直竖。但这种风格反而成为吸引读者的魅力，使他人气始终不衰。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8216&rangeEnd=8279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8216&rangeEnd=8279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_14913-14942",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14913-14942",
      "markText": "阴兽栖息于幽暗之中，屏住气息，犹如哑巴般不发出半点儿声响。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14913&rangeEnd=14942",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14913&rangeEnd=14942"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_27_11872-11930",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "11872-11930",
      "markText": "结果，绢代女士却羞赧地低下头，而后抬眼看了我一下，随即满脸通红。我立刻心领神会。万右卫门先生在某方面的行为相当残暴。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=11872&rangeEnd=11930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=11872&rangeEnd=11930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_27_6395-6477",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "6395-6477",
      "markText": "若问原因，这就是我长久以来梦想的情景。那尸体仿佛在黑暗中独自绽放的鲜红花朵般，充满了魔力，那是美妙的血的艺术。我朝思暮想的就是这幅光景啊！真是从天而降的完美模特儿。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=6395&rangeEnd=6477",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=6395&rangeEnd=6477"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_4_47266-47342",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "47266-47342",
      "markText": "不管静子是不是杀人凶手，我只能诅咒自己那狭隘的道德观。这世上有比爱情更纯洁、更美丽的事物吗？难道我不是以道学者顽固的心态，残酷地杀死那清雅美丽的爱情吗？",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=754057&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=47266&rangeEnd=47342",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1f432c405b81891f4383a5a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=47266&rangeEnd=47342"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "754057_15_2899-2930",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2899-2930",
      "markText": "因此，这个房间终年没有日照，而这里就是他的起居室、书房兼卧室。",
